{"tid":1632052,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【黨鐵裝修建議】","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:36:57.000Z","uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b7603bf9e6f6310d8b08845d7953ac46e372a19c","tid":1632052,"uid":266045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:33.000Z","msg":"由於黨鐵係靠管理物業賺錢嘅，<br />\n我哋好似應該target返喺佢嘅物業度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BDZmAHu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBDZmAHu.jpg&h=35d3479e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身為一個讀過下建築法例嘅廢青，<br />\n我有咁嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">由於火魔法師好少喺室內表演，</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足可以幫手裝修下黨鐵商場天花同中庭之間伸落嚟嘅防煙玻璃/結構</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHDbdu6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHDbdu6.jpg&h=badad5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以同時邀請到屋宇署同埋消防處嚟飲咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講消防處阿sir好嚴厲㗎<br />\n&hearts;場面一定好溫馨&hearts;"},{"pid":"a8bf4c16354d3735dcaf74e0e049c8db7a970141","tid":1632052,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"【警世良言】中共劇本係想抹黑「香港人打砸搶燒」，然後種族滅絕！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623758</a><br />\n<br />\n毛澤東：西藏越亂越好，可以鍛鍊軍隊，可以鍛鍊 基本群眾，又為將來平叛和實施改革提供充足的理由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530340</a><br />\n<br />\n大家要冷靜, 理性分析, 我地唔可以變成中共口中既暴徒<br />\n<br />\n我地要外國幫手先可以贏, 佢地全部人都係左膠, 所以畫面要做好啲, 唔好咁多裝修, 要多裝飾<br />\n<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">無理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">8964</span>, 之後被國際制裁<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">合理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">新彊</span>, 然後就沒有了然後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">外國要有合理既藉口制裁中共</span></span>"},{"pid":"56822df9a88b772b4cdc4c44f62625963e745c19","tid":1632052,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}